o brother , where art thou ? is a 2000 american drama film directed by joel coen and starring george clooney , john turturro , and tim robbins . the film was produced by joel coen and joel coen . the film was directed by joel coen and written by joel coen and ethan coen . the film was nominated for the academy award for best foreign language film at the 74th academy awards , but was not accepted as a nominee .